{"about_the_game":"This is a game centered around surviving in a harsh, cold environment, offering you the ultimate test of survival.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn the game, you will tackle the following primary tasks:<br />\r\nMining and logging: Gather resources to sustain survival and craft various items using these materials to create a habitable environment.<br />\r\nCrop cultivation: Cultivate crops in adverse conditions to meet food requirements.<br />\r\nAnimal husbandry: Acquire additional food and resources through animal breeding.<br />\r\nRecruiting NPCs: Employ assistants to help you complete various tasks and work.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou will need to carefully modify the environment, using a heating system to ensure a comfortable living environment for both yourself and the NPCs. However, you must also be mindful of the pollution generated by the heating system to maintain a delicate balance.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAdditionally, the game provides main storyline missions to guide you to explore the game world more deeply, but these missions are not mandatory.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game offers both single-player mode and local network multiplayer mode, enabling you to cooperate with friends to face the challenges of this cold world together and create even more excitement and enjoyment.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Day","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2681650/501ef481f65d2da62e451bce518d494cd27fad2b.jpg"},{"name":"Day 10","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2681650/501ef481f65d2da62e451bce518d494cd27fad2b.jpg"},{"name":"Day 100","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2681650/501ef481f65d2da62e451bce518d494cd27fad2b.jpg"},{"name":"Camp","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2681650/501ef481f65d2da62e451bce518d494cd27fad2b.jpg"},{"name":"Hamlet","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/s